<div class="modal fade display-modal-lg" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="LargeModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg" role="document">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-body">
        <button type="button" class="close dark" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
        <div class="card col-md-12">
          <div class="card-body p-0 row overflow-hidden">
            <div class="offset-lg-1 col-lg-10">
              <div class="mt-2">
                <h1 class="font-weight-bold">Setting up your account</h1>
                <h4 class="mt-4">We're going to take you on a journey, where you will hop over to our partner's site, Stripe.com, to start your account set up.</h4>
                <a href="https://stripe.com" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm rounded mb-3">Who are Stripe?</a>
                <p>Stripe.com are one of the biggest tech companies in the world. They will be taking care of all the online payments, whilst maintaining the highest levels of security.</p>
                <p>You'll be be entering your business details (name, address, etc) and details of all owners/directors in the company, or just your own, if you're a solo founder.</p>
                <p>So you'll need:</p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                  <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary mr-1"></i> Business details...</li>
                  <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary mr-1"></i> Significant people details...</li>
                  <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary mr-1"></i> Some form of ID (a scan/photo of your passport or driving license)</li>
                  <li><i class="fa fa-check text-primary mr-1"></i> And finally your bank account number so we can pay all your money</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Once you're done, you'll be able to take instant card payments from all your new bookings.</p>
                <p>This can take up to 15 minutes but you can always save and continue later.</p>
                <div class="text-center my-4">
                  <%= link_to stripe_account_link, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg rounded uppercase" do %>
                    Setup my account
                  <% end %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
